{
  "stem": "16163.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we took, I think, the train back home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm trying to.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think the English version would be [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 'Curly Head,' something like that, a child with curls.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think the actress was a child actress something, like Shirley-- what was her name?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Shirley Temple was, at the same time-- approximately at the same time, right?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], that I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think it must have wanted to see that movie, that maybe I read the book, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the movie.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's the last time I went to the movie there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, I never did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One of those.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember three homes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The home where I was born, which was a very huge, large apartment, very modern furniture-- you know, the Bauhaus type what they had in Europe at that time already in the '20s.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we moved from there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], 36.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] Street, 36.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I must have been about seven or eight years old, because we had to leave that particular apartment.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't my parents' house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had an apartment there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, as a matter of fact, that Gunter, and his mother and father, and his brother, also lived in the same building.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had to move.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we were Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That started very early there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we moved to a different area in that small town, like from one end to the other town.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- but very close to each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had, like, an apartment few blocks-- not even few-- a few houses down from where we lived.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was a smaller apartment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But, you know, when you're a child, you're getting-- you don't know any better.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
